name:                todobackend-scotty
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            Todobackend implementation using Scotty
description:         Please see README.md
license:             MIT
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Joel Hermanns
maintainer:          joel.hermanns@gmail.com
